The,Appaloosa,API,allows,developers,to,access,information,on,applications,in,their,online,app,store,Appaloosa,is,a,mobile,application,management,and,distribution,service,for,iOS,Android,and,Windows,Phone,Users,can,customize,and,rebrand,their,own,app,stores,and,send,push,notifications,to,their,customers,Appaloosa,also,provides,analytics,tools,for,looking,at,detailed,app,and,version,download,statistics